WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.288
Welcome to Team Management.

00:02.288 --> 00:10.288
Invite Members: Send email invitations to technicians, administrators, and even client contacts.

00:10.288 --> 00:13.339
Each invite includes role selection.

00:13.339 --> 00:21.339
Assign Roles: Control permissions precisely — View Only for clients, Edit for technicians, Admin for managers, and Owner for full control.

00:21.339 --> 00:24.559
Licences: Manage your seat allocation.

00:24.559 --> 00:32.559
Add or remove team members, transfer licences between users, and monitor usage from the admin panel.

00:32.559 --> 00:35.695
Your team stays organised and secure.